WEBVTT

1
01:29:04.090 --> 01:29:06.120 
我的小百合她知道收音机里
My River Lily who knew all the words

2
01:29:06.120 --> 01:29:09.110 
每一首歌的歌词
to every song that came over the radio.

3
01:29:11.100 --> 01:29:14.110 
我回地球看过她三次
I returned to Earth to see her three times.

4
01:29:14.110 --> 01:29:16.590 
我知道如果我再回去一次
And I knew if I returned a 4th...

5
01:29:16.590 --> 01:29:18.580 
我就舍不得回来了
I'd never leave.

6
01:29:19.060 --> 01:29:20.130 
这个扩张计划
The Expansion...

7
01:29:22.100 --> 01:29:24.130 
我存在的理由将毁于一旦 所以
the reason for my very existence would be over, so...

8
01:29:24.130 --> 01:29:27.050 
我做了我该做的事儿
I did what I had to do.

9
01:29:27.090 --> 01:29:28.130 
但
But...

10
01:29:29.560 --> 01:29:32.630 
把肿瘤放进她大脑的时候我也很难过
it broke my heart to put that tumor in her head.

